# ── WG13 repository ignores ──────────────────────────────────────────────
# Repo root is "D:\world gen 13". Docs + the wg-13 Godot project are tracked.
# The archive and all heavy/generated data are NOT.

# Archived WG9/WG10 material (~97 GB: old code, DEMs, generated worlds).
# Kept on disk for reference; never committed.
/archive/

# Move manifests are bookkeeping for the archive operation, not project source.
/_manifest/

# ── Godot ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Editor cache / imported assets / per-machine state.
wg-13/.godot/
wg-13/android/
wg-13/*.translation

# ── Rust / gdext (created at M1.1) ───────────────────────────────────────
# Build output for the GDExtension crate. Can be huge; always reproducible.
**/target/
**/*.rs.bk
Cargo.lock.bak

# Compiled GDExtension libraries land next to the .gdextension file when built.
# Track the .gdextension manifest; ignore the per-platform binaries.
*.dll.lib
*.pdb
*.exp

# ── Capture output (scratch evidence, regenerable) ───────────────────────
# PNGs from capture scripts are reviewable scratch, not source. Gate evidence
# lives in DRIFT_LOG narrative + the live scene. Don't bloat the repo with them.
wg-13/_captures/

# ── OS / editor noise ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
.DS_Store
*.swp
